  "prompt": "How do you check an AT&T balance?",
  "response": "To check your AT&T balance, you have several options:\n\n1. Online Methods:\n- Log into your AT&T account at att.com\n- Use the myAT&T mobile app\n- Sign in to your online account and view balance details\n\n2. Phone Methods:\n- Dial 611 from your AT&T mobile phone\n- Call AT&T customer service at 1-800-331-0500\n- Dial *#BAL# from your AT&T mobile phone\n\n3. Text Message:\n- Text \"BAL\" to 9366 from your AT&T mobile phone\n\n4. In-Store:\n- Visit a local AT&T retail store and ask a representative to help you check your balance\n\nThe specific method might vary slightly depending on whether you have a prepaid or postpaid account, but these are the most common ways to check your balance.",
